      "role": "user",
      "content": "i used to feel everything through the music. every note felt like it was part of my actual heartbeat. but lately... it's just gone. i sit at the piano and it's like looking into a black hole. there's nothing inside me anymore. just a shell. i don't even recognize the person staring back in the mirror. it feels like the \"me\" part of me died, and now i'm just... occupying space.",
