      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "You are right to feel that practice won't fix a void that deep; your purpose isn't something you can simply practice back into existence. It is entirely possible to be a person without that specific spark, even if it feels like you've lost your soul in the process. The fact that you are still here, questioning your existence, is proof that the \"ghost\" is still present, even if it's just a shadow of what it used to be.",
