    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but being a \"shadow\" feels so exhausting. it's like i'm just carrying around this heavy, empty body that doesn't even belong to me anymore. if the core of me is gone, what is the point of the rest of it? why does the vessel have to keep going when there's nothing left to hold inside?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
